      "content": "i dont know. \"defiance\" just sounds exhausting. like, why am i fighting for a future that isn't even coming? it feels less like defiance and more like just being stubborn while everything falls apart. if the end is inevitable, why bother struggling through all the pain and watching everything die? it seems more logical to just... not be part of it. to just stop.",
